Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getNetWeight(25.10)                                        getNetWeight(25.10)

Name
       getNetWeight - Retrieves the net weight values for the specified nets

Syntax
        getNetWeight

       [-help]

       {-all | <netName><...> }

       Retrieves  the  net  weight  values for the specified nets. You can use
       this command after running the specifyNetWeightcommand.

Parameters
       -all   Retrieves the net weight value for all nets.

              Data_type: bool, required

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information for each getNetWeight parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man getNetWeight

       <netName>
              Retrieves the net weight value for all specified nets.

              Data_type: string, required

Related Information
              * specifyNetWeight

              * deleteNetWeight

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

